<p><strong>16. For B2C brands, email marketing ranks as the number 1 ROI channel.</strong>
Source: <a href="https://www.hubspot.com/marketing-statistics">HubSpot</a>, 2026
It outperforms paid social, content marketing, and display ads.</p>
