<h2>Email Open Rate Statistics</h2>
<p><strong>17. The average email open rate across all industries is 43.46% in 2026.</strong>
Source: <a href="https://www.activecampaign.com/blog/activecampaign-email-benchmarks">ActiveCampaign</a>, 2026
Apple Mail Privacy Protection inflates this number. Focus on click rates for accuracy.</p>
<p><strong>18. Non-profit organizations have the highest open rate at 52.38%.</strong>
Source: <a href="https://www.activecampaign.com/blog/activecampaign-email-benchmarks">ActiveCampaign</a>, 2026
