<p><strong>19. Health and fitness emails average a 47.81% open rate.</strong>
Source: <a href="https://www.activecampaign.com/blog/activecampaign-email-benchmarks">ActiveCampaign</a>, 2026
This sector benefits from high subscriber engagement and personal relevance.</p>
<p><strong>20. E-commerce emails average a 32.67% open rate.</strong>
Source: <a href="https://www.activecampaign.com/blog/activecampaign-email-benchmarks">ActiveCampaign</a>, 2026
Lower than average. Competitive inboxes and frequent promotional sends drive this down.</p>
<p><strong>21. Personalized subject lines increase open rates by 50%.</strong>
Source: <a href="https://www.oberlo.com/blog/email-marketing-statistics">Oberlo</a>, 2025
