<p><strong>22. Welcome emails achieve a 68.6% open rate.</strong>
Source: <a href="https://influencermarketinghub.com/email-marketing-statistics/">Influencer Marketing Hub</a>, 2025
The first email after signup gets the highest engagement. Make it count.</p>
