Source: <a href="https://www.activecampaign.com/blog/activecampaign-email-benchmarks">ActiveCampaign</a>, 2026
CTOR measures how many openers actually click. It is a better signal than open rate alone.</p>
<p><strong>24. The legal industry leads click-through rates at 4.90%.</strong>
Source: <a href="https://www.klaviyo.com/uk/blog/email-marketing-benchmarks-open-click-and-conversion-rates">Klaviyo</a>, 2026
